    <!-- Chosen Palette: Warm Neutral (bg-neutral-50, text-neutral-800) with Indigo (indigo-500) accent -->
    <!-- Application Structure Plan: Designed a non-linear, skills-first SPA. A top "Skills Dashboard" (with a Radar Chart and interactive skill grid) serves as the primary navigation. This is more user-friendly for a recruiter than the source's linear list. Users can explore by skill (e.g., "Regulatory Analysis") which then highlights the relevant "Case Studies" below, or explore by project, which highlights the skills used. This two-way data binding (via JS) directly links claims (skills) to evidence (projects), optimizing for user understanding and synthesis. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 1. (Source: 12 Key Competencies) -> Goal: Inform/Organize/Relate -> Viz: Interactive JS grid + Chart.js Radar Chart. Interaction: onClick on skill highlights related projects. Justification: Synthesizes 12 scattered data points into a single, interactive dashboard, directly answering "What are your skills?". 2. (Source: 3 Case Studies) -> Goal: Inform/Organize -> Viz: 3-Card layout with a JS-powered "display area". Interaction: onClick on card loads project details (Problem, Solution, Outcome) and highlights related skills. Justification: Converts static text into an interactive "drill-down" experience, maintaining the single-page flow. -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
